trans-unit.source: InlineCollection defines the allowable child content of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Span"></xref>, and <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock"></xref> elements.
trans-unit.target: InlineCollection definerer tillatte barnet innholdet i den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Span"> </xref>, og <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock"> </xref> elementer.

trans-unit.source: InlineCollection creation is only permitted inside an element that owns an InlineCollection, such as a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock> or a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph>.
trans-unit.target: Oppretting av InlineCollection er bare tillatt i et element som eier en InlineCollection, for eksempel <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>eller <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph>.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>

trans-unit.source: As such, an InlineCollection cannot be instantiated directly and has no default or overloaded constructor.
trans-unit.target: En InlineCollection kan ikke startes direkte har ingen standardverdi og overlastet konstruktør.
